00:14:29.260 --> 00:14:30.420
Father!

148
00:14:37.380 --> 00:14:39.460
Son. my son.. how are you?

149
00:14:40.260 --> 00:14:43.780
Why haven't you eaten?

150
00:14:43.940 --> 00:14:46.100
Why doesn't Mummy
