152
00:14:51.540 --> 00:14:53.940
Papa. please.. Papa. please.

153
00:14:54.020 --> 00:14:54.940
Son.

154
00:14:56.540 --> 00:15:01.060
Isn't she my mother?
- She's very much your mother.

155
00:15:02.260 --> 00:15:07.260
You were born of her womb.
- So why doesn't she love..?

156
00:15:07.340 --> 00:15:11.020
You'll have an answer
to all your questions. son.

157
00:15:11.580 --> 00:15:12.420
The day you grow up.

158
00:15:12.499 --> 00:15:17.859
Take me to Mummy. Please. Papa!

159
00:15:28.660 --> 00:15:32.460
I looked everywhere else for you.
but when I couldn't find you..

160
00:15:32.540 --> 00:15:34.340
I understood.
that my friend must be here..

161
00:15:34.660 --> 00:15:39.540
..in this Rajput mansion
thinking about his mother

162
00:15:40.780 --> 00:15:46.340
What happened today that
you came here to meet your past?

163
00:15:49.780 --> 00:15:51.660
You still remember her face?

164
00:15:52.860 --> 00:15:54.780
Can anyone forget
how his mother looked?

165
00:15:55.860 --> 00:16:01.580
Wherever she comes from. I
just want her to hold me to her bosom.

166
00:16:03.420 --> 00:16:07.380
