176
00:17:13.920 --> 00:17:15.000
Oh my God!

177
00:17:16.120 --> 00:17:21.800
Meeting Suraj during the day.
nobody could ever say that he..

178
00:17:22.160 --> 00:17:27.200
That he's drowned in
darkness by night. isn't it?

179
00:17:28.520 --> 00:17:34.840
A mother leaving her own child?
Why. grandma?

180
00:17:35.120 --> 00:17:37.880
None of us knows that.

181
00:17:40.080 --> 00:17:42.040
Neither does Suraj.

182
00:17:43.480 --> 00:17:48.320
When one finds no answers
to some burning questions..

183
00:17:49.080 --> 00:17:53.480
..man can neither live nor die.

184
00:18:20.220 --> 00:18:23.860
"No fairy ever arrives.."

185
00:18:24.180 --> 00:18:27.660
"To light up my dreams.."

186
00:18:28.380 --> 00:18:35.580
"So sing me a lullaby
and put me to sleep"

187
00:18:36.220 --> 00:18:44.060
"In your arms. come.. put me to sleep"

188
00:18:44.140 --> 00:18:47.700
