190
00:18:52.260 --> 00:18:55.620
"Why do you make me cry.."

191
00:18:55.700 --> 00:18:57.780
"Come to me.."

192
00:18:58.140 --> 00:19:01.740
"Come to me.."

193
00:19:02.140 --> 00:19:06.060
"Come to me.."

194
00:19:06.220 --> 00:19:10.100
"Come to me.."

195
00:19:16.280 --> 00:19:24.080
"The earth has gone to sleep.
so have the skies.."

196
00:19:31.880 --> 00:19:35.400
Mother. I won't let you leave again.

197
00:19:59.200 --> 00:20:02.120
Have you ever thought?
If Suraj (the Sun)..

198
00:20:02.200 --> 00:20:05.960
