how dark it would be around us?

199
00:20:08.440 --> 00:20:15.400
Maybe you don't know.
but your sorrow bothers others too.

200
00:20:17.600 --> 00:20:21.160
Besides. God gives
no human being only sorrow.

201
00:20:22.040 --> 00:20:26.840
Apart from sorrow. he also
gives man some happiness.. and love.

202
00:20:27.680 --> 00:20:30.600
It's just that man can't
see it happening around him.

203
00:20:32.880 --> 00:20:36.120
Instead of drowning yourself
in liquor. you ought to seek out..

204
00:20:36.520 --> 00:20:40.440
..that happiness and love.
There's another side to life.

205
00:20:40.840 --> 00:20:44.280
It's very beautiful. Try living that.

206
00:20:46.220 --> 00:20:47.140
I am sorry.

207
00:20:47.780 --> 00:20:50.900
If I have said something I
shouldn't have. please do forgive me.

208
00:20:51.780 --> 00:20:54.220
Because I consider
you to be my friend. I..

209
00:21:06.740 --> 00:21:10.300
I ought to thank you. not God. - Why?

210
00:21:10.500 --> 00:21:13.140
Because I've got an admission
in the college because of you.

211
00:21:13.420 --> 00:21:13.980
Son.. - Lady..? You're cold.

212
00:21:14.300 --> 00:21:15.540
Lady..? - How are you. son.

213
00:21:15.620 --> 00:21:16.500
You're cold.

214
00:21:16.580 --> 00:21:19.820
I went up the hill.
it was very chilly there.

215
00:21:19.900 --> 00:21:23.300
It was so cold.
I thought maybe I should walk around..

216
00:21:23.380 --> 00:21:24.500
I'd feel a bit warm.

217
00:21:26.380 --> 00:21:30.060
Go and buy a blanket immediately.
- May you live long. son.

218
00:21:30.500 --> 00:21:35.420
May God give you
so much of happiness..

219
00:21:35.500 --> 00:21:36.860
..it must last you a lifetime.

220
00:21:38.380 --> 00:21:41.380
Who was she? - A grief-stricken woman.

221
00:21:42.620 --> 00:21:46.260
All her life. she did people's
dishes and washed their clothes.

222
00:21:46.340 --> 00:21:49.180
Know why? For her son.

223
00:21:49.820 --> 00:21:53.900
And the day he grew up.
he left his mother.

224
00:21:55.060 --> 00:21:59.780
Ever since. she goes around
begging like a mad woman.

225
00:22:00.260 --> 00:22:01.380
That's so sad.

226
00:22:02.660 --> 00:22:07.700
What a strange world.
- Yes. it's a strange world.

227
00:22:08.700 --> 00:22:11.060
There are sons walking out on..

228
00:22:11.140 --> 00:22:13.620
