Lonely. in dreams of you.
I've been writing poetry

743
01:02:08.400 --> 01:02:16.920
"You have come down on earth for me.
O celestial beauty"

744
01:02:17.480 --> 01:02:26.360
"Lonely. in dreams of you.
I've been writing poetry"

745
01:02:30.240 --> 01:02:34.640
"Now that you have seen me.
do not ignore me"

746
01:02:34.720 --> 01:02:40.360
"This is the time to romance"

747
01:02:40.960 --> 01:02:45.280
"I need your love"

748
01:02:45.880 --> 01:02:50.240
"You are my beloved"

749
01:02:50.640 --> 01:02:54.280
"You are the fragrance in the air"

750
01:02:54.600 --> 01:03:03.680
"Every moment. I think of you"

751
01:03:13.120 --> 01:03:18.600
On your face a blush beams.
Yet you are mischievous.

752
01:03:19.200 --> 01:03:21.640
There's indifference in your eyes.

753
01:03:21.960 --> 01:03:24.200
Yet there is love in your heart.

754
01:03:28.920 --> 01:03:33.120
"On your face a blush beams"

755
01:03:33.320 --> 01:03:37.400
"Yet you are mischievous"

756
01:03:37.920 --> 01:03:42.040
"There's indifference in your eyes"

757
01:03:42.200 --> 01:03:46.360
"Yet there is love in your heart"

758
01:03:49.280 --> 01:03:53.360
"You are so full of love.
you are so innocent"

759
01:03:53.560 --> 01:03:59.520
"The hues of my beloved are unique"

760
01:03:59.800 --> 01:04:04.240
"I need your love"

761
01:04:04.760 --> 01:04:09.040
"You are my beloved"

762
01:04:09.320 --> 01:04:13.080
"You are the fragrance in the air"

763
01:04:13.240 --> 01:04:22.160
"You are the one
I think of every moment"

764
01:04:23.640 --> 01:04:27.800
"Without seeing you. I swear.."

765
01:04:28.040 --> 01:04:32.120
"I can't breathe"

766
01:04:32.440 --> 01:04:39.240
"My heart's bound in a spell.."

767
01:04:40.400 --> 01:04:44.440
"..that your love has cast"

768
01:04:45.000 --> 01:04:49.040
"..that your love has cast"

769
01:06:00.160 --> 01:06:03.920
You're Suraj. aren't you?
My son's friend

770
01:06:04.960 --> 01:06:07.200
See? I recognised you. didn't I son?

771
01:06:07.400 --> 01:06:09.960
Yes mother. you've recognised me.

772
01:06:10.040 --> 01:06:13.640
I knew the moron wouldn't
come to receive me.

773
01:06:13.720 --> 01:06:15.600
Let's see how long he hides.

774
01:06:16.120 --> 01:06:18.240
Shall we..? - Let's go.

775
01:07:00.260 --> 01:07:01.340
Mother..

776
01:07:04.140 --> 01:07:05.620
..you recall something?

777
01:07:07.820 --> 01:07:10.860
No.. nothing.

778
01:07:14.420 --> 01:07:16.820
Mother! - My darling.

779
01:07:16.900 --> 01:07:19.700
Thank you for coming.
Love you.. Love you..

780
01:07:19.780 --> 01:07:21.140
Leave me. I'm going to fall.

781
01:07:21.220 --> 01:07:23.300
I'm with you.
- What are you doing? Silly boy.

782
01:07:23.380 --> 01:07:26.780
I love you. - I love you too.

783
01:07:33.060 --> 01:07:34.020
Suraj.

784
01:07:35.900 --> 01:07:37.220
You are up so early?

785
01:07:39.900 --> 01:07:43.900
You seem to have
stayed up all night. son.

786
01:07:45.420 --> 01:07:47.900
What's the matter?
Why haven't you slept?

787
01:07:48.820 --> 01:07:53.140
Mother is here. father.

788
01:07:56.780 --> 01:07:58.140
Yes Father.

789
01:07:58.980 --> 01:08:04.060
I can tell mother
that I'm her son. can I?

790
01:08:06.820 --> 01:08:09.260
No Suraj. no. - Why not. Father?

791
01:08:09.340 --> 01:08:12.460
Look Suraj. I don't want..
- What do you don't want?

792
01:08:13.220 --> 01:08:19.180
What don't you want? I couldn't
tell Raja that I'm his brother.

793
01:08:19.260 --> 01:08:24.580
Because mother hasn't told him
about me. Besides. I was apprehensive.

794
01:08:24.660 --> 01:08:28.820
Now that mother is here.
why can't I tell her?

795
01:08:29.220 --> 01:08:33.580
Father. I want to embrace mother.

796
01:08:34.660 --> 01:08:38.220
Instead of embracing you.
why did she forsake you?

797
01:08:39.260 --> 01:08:40.700
Why did she leave you and go away?

798
01:08:41.860 --> 01:08:43.180
What if she hates you again like..

799
01:08:43.260 --> 01:08:44.500
..she hated you when you were little?

800
01:08:46.420 --> 01:08:47.260
Will you be able to stand it?

801
01:08:48.580 --> 01:08:50.460
No son. you won't be
able to stand her slight.

802
01:08:51.140 --> 01:08:52.100
It'll make life miserable.

803
01:08:53.020 --> 01:08:57.380
Father.. - You'll tell
your mother nothing. Suraj.

804
01:08:58.140 --> 01:09:02.700
You will not say a word to her.
I place you under my oath.

805
01:09:16.300 --> 01:09:20.780
You are adopting this child.
so I told you the truth.

806
01:09:21.620 --> 01:09:25.540
It's for you to decide. Doesn't
the mother and son need to stay apart?

807
01:09:34.300 --> 01:09:36.500
Mr. Balwant. this is the reason..

808
01:09:36.580 --> 01:09:39.180
..why I had to convince his mother
that he is dead.

809
01:09:41.340 --> 01:09:45.820
I pray. the day never comes when..

810
01:09:46.460 --> 01:09:48.420
.. they would get face
to face with each other.

811
01:09:49.900 --> 01:09:50.980
It'd be devastating.

812
01:09:56.380 --> 01:09:59.580
What's this? I asked you
to take the oblations first.

813
01:10:00.540 --> 01:10:02.460
Want..? - There's
barely anything to eat.

814
01:10:03.300 --> 01:10:05.580
When will you learn table manners?

815
01:10:06.100 --> 01:10:08.140
Suraj takes care of me more than you.

816
01:10:08.220 --> 01:10:12.060
It seems he's my son. not you.
- Suraj is..

817
01:10:12.260 --> 01:10:17.020
Ma.. greetings.
- Suraj! Come son. sit here.

818
01:10:17.500 --> 01:10:19.900
Amazing. big brother.
We were talking about you.

819
01:10:20.220 --> 01:10:21.980
You're going to live
at least a hundred years.

820
01:10:23.620 --> 01:10:28.540
No jokes. son.
It's true. we were talking about you.

821
01:10:28.620 --> 01:10:32.420
Talking about me? What were
you talking about me. mother?

822
01:10:32.660 --> 01:10:36.900
That. Suraj is a nice boy.
and I'm bad.

823
01:10:37.860 --> 01:10:40.140
I think you're going to
steal my mother from me. big brother.

824
01:10:41.820 --> 01:10:45.460
Mother belongs to the elder
brother first. As for stealing her..

825
01:10:47.300 --> 01:10:50.100
..the younger brother does it.
Right mother?

826
01:10:51.320 --> 01:10:55.360
I almost forgot.
Father said. it'd be nice.

827
01:10:55.440 --> 01:10:57.800
if you come over and meet Sapna.

828
01:10:57.880 --> 01:11:00.080
Nice? It'd be great. big brother.

829
01:11:00.160 --> 01:11:01.480
Brilliant idea mother!

830
01:11:01.560 --> 01:11:06.960
Are you mad? Sapna isn't
a doll that I'll inspect and try out.

831
01:11:07.920 --> 01:11:11.520
Since you and Suraj like her.
I too must like her.

832
01:11:11.840 --> 01:11:14.680
Yes son. I'd like to see her once.

833
01:11:15.200 --> 01:11:16.560
Why not organize a party?

834
01:11:16.800 --> 01:11:18.400
That'd give me an
opportunity to meet her.

835
01:11:18.480 --> 01:11:20.360
Brilliant idea mother!

836
01:11:21.880 --> 01:11:23.280
Holy offerings. madam. - Thanks.

837
01:11:24.280 --> 01:11:25.600
Here Eat.

838
01:11:27.520 --> 01:11:29.640
Here.. no. let me feed you. son.

839
01:11:43.220 --> 01:11:46.780
Suraj. she is Sapna. isn't she?
- Yes mother.

840
01:11:47.420 --> 01:11:49.100
Sapna.. - Mother.

841
01:11:49.900 --> 01:11:50.860
Greetings.

842
01:11:56.620 --> 01:12:00.020
Go on. dear. Raja is over there.

843
01:12:00.660 --> 01:12:01.580
Yes.

844
01:12:01.660 --> 01:12:04.540
Suppose a fairy comes down to..

845
01:12:04.620 --> 01:12:07.140
..earth in the form of a girl.
what would you do?

846
01:12:08.060 --> 01:12:08.860
There she is.

847
01:12:08.940 --> 01:12:11.660
See.. ladies and ladies.

848
01:12:11.860 --> 01:12:14.620
My love my life.. My fairy.

849
01:12:15.460 --> 01:12:19.740
What'd you have done
had Sapna not fallen for you?

850
01:12:19.820 --> 01:12:21.700
I'd have married you.

851
01:12:23.320 --> 01:12:26.080
You left the city as
if you vanished into thin air.

852
01:12:26.920 --> 01:12:29.640
I had to leave for business' sake.

853
01:12:29.920 --> 01:12:31.760
And had to return for Raja's sake.

854
01:12:31.840 --> 01:12:34.960
Had to. for the sake
of my only son's happiness.

855
01:12:35.720 --> 01:12:38.240
Yes you are right.

856
01:13:48.500 --> 01:13:51.020
Raja. why did Suraj..?

857
01:13:53.140 --> 01:13:58.620
Happiness eludes him. mother.
Some old wound must've resurfaced.

858
01:14:00.740 --> 01:14:02.220
He gives his love to the world.

859
01:14:03.260 --> 01:14:08.140
But he has gained nothing but anguish.

860
01:14:14.220 --> 01:14:18.060
"My tears. I have suppressed"

861
01:14:18.220 --> 01:14:22.100
"My life has been miserable.."

862
01:14:22.180 --> 01:14:30.020
"Oh. how do I say how
helpless how I've been.."

863
01:14:30.260 --> 01:14:37.860
"You are so near. yet so far.."

864
01:14:37.940 --> 01:14:42.140
"I want to you call you mother.."

865
01:14:42.220 --> 01:14:46.180
"I wish to embrace you.."

866
01:14:46.260 --> 01:14:49.620
"Oh. how do I tell you.."

867
01:14:49.700 --> 01:14:55.980
"My constraints.."

868
01:14:56.180 --> 01:15:00.180
"My constraints.."

869
01:15:00.260 --> 01:15:04.020
"My constraints.."

870
01:15:29.420 --> 01:15:35.340
You are my son. Sonu.

871
01:15:42.260 --> 01:15:42.900
Mother.

872
01:15:46.620 --> 01:15:52.500
Which means your father
lied to me that you were..

873
01:15:57.260 --> 01:15:58.180
My son.

874
01:16:05.780 --> 01:16:06.940
My darling.

875
01:16:10.380 --> 01:16:14.620
My boy.. my son.

876
01:16:35.740 --> 01:16:36.380
Mother..

877
01:16:36.580 --> 01:16:40.540
Go away.. get out of my sight!

878
01:16:41.980 --> 01:16:45.900
When will you stop chasing me?
Get out of here. I say!

879
01:16:47.740 --> 01:16:51.700
Do you know how much
I hate your very sight?

880
01:16:51.780 --> 01:16:56.340
Why do you hate me. mother?
Since childhood I've been pining..

881
01:16:56.420 --> 01:17:03.060
..and searching for an answer.
What makes you detest me?

882
01:17:04.460 --> 01:17:08.260
Why do you hate me? Tell me. why?

883
01:17:08.340 --> 01:17:14.140
Because you're not human.
You are a monster!

884
01:17:16.580 --> 01:17:20.180
Yograj! - Yograj..?

885
01:17:20.380 --> 01:17:25.820
You're a beast! You have
no right to live among humans!

886
01:17:26.100 --> 01:17:30.940
You ought to be behind bars!
And I shall get you behind bars.

887
01:17:31.500 --> 01:17:33.420
Your Honour..

888
01:17:33.500 --> 01:17:36.460
I have witnessed this devil's crime.

889
01:17:38.500 --> 01:17:42.380
I saw it! He raped that poor girl..

890
01:17:42.660 --> 01:17:46.740
..and then mercilessly
slit the innocent's throat.

891
01:17:47.460 --> 01:17:52.980
Look at him. Your Honour.
Look at that vicious grin.

892
01:17:54.220 --> 01:17:58.220
But I'm not afraid of him.
Despite his threats..

893
01:17:58.300 --> 01:18:02.140
..I have come to the court
so that justice may be done.

894
01:18:11.320 --> 01:18:14.600
Mr Raja.
if she doesn't come around soon..

895
01:18:14.680 --> 01:18:16.240
..her life could be in danger.

896
01:18:16.760 --> 01:18:18.760
I think she has received
a terrible shock.

897
01:18:18.840 --> 01:18:23.480
What shock. doctor? Impossible.
She was fine and happy yesterday.

898
01:18:23.840 --> 01:18:26.880
How come all of a sudden..?
- No. this is not a sudden shock.

899
01:18:27.400 --> 01:18:29.960
I think she has had these
kind of bouts before too.

900
01:18:33.800 --> 01:18:36.840
Have you contacted your
family doctor? - Not yet.

901
01:18:37.440 --> 01:18:41.800
He's attending a conference
in America. But we're trying.

902
01:18:41.880 --> 01:18:45.120
Please contact him
as soon as possible. Ok.

903
01:18:49.480 --> 01:18:53.880
What the doctor says just beats me.

904
01:19:00.260 --> 01:19:04.700
Let it be dark. Father.
I can't stand the light.

905
01:19:08.820 --> 01:19:12.740
I know you are extremely hurt. son.

906
01:19:15.340 --> 01:19:22.220
But to stand the pain God
has give you a strong heart. too.

907
01:19:24.100 --> 01:19:26.340
You must step out
of the darkness. son.

908
01:19:28.100 --> 01:19:30.100
You got to search the
path of happiness on your own.

909
01:19:30.940 --> 01:19:33.980
How is my mother? - Same as before.

910
01:19:35.100 --> 01:19:39.540
The doctor it is imperative
that she comes around. else..

911
01:19:39.620 --> 01:19:44.180
Nothing is happening to my mother.
Nothing! She'll be fine

912
01:19:45.540 --> 01:19:49.100
Goddess Mother.
I never understood you.

913
01:19:50.420 --> 01:19:53.860
But you know me.

914
01:19:54.900 --> 01:19:57.900
Please help my mother recover.

915
01:20:12.340 --> 01:20:15.940
Big brother.
you never fail to surprise me.

916
01:20:17.420 --> 01:20:21.140
Every time you come up with
something that has no real reasons.

917
01:20:22.900 --> 01:20:27.500
I could never imagine
you wouldn't come to see mother.

918
01:20:29.180 --> 01:20:32.660
Though I felt like coming.
I couldn't gather enough courage.

919
01:20:33.580 --> 01:20:35.500
I can't see her in this state.

920
01:20:36.460 --> 01:20:38.100
Why did she go to your house?

921
01:20:39.020 --> 01:20:42.020
I walked out of the party.
and she felt bad.

922
01:20:42.420 --> 01:20:43.980
So she came to call me back.

923
01:20:44.860 --> 01:20:48.740
But what happened there that
gave her such a terrible shock?

924
01:20:49.860 --> 01:20:51.740
That's the question worrying me.

925
01:20:52.140 --> 01:20:54.860
I don't know why she started yelling.

926
01:20:55.740 --> 01:20:59.100
But Suraj.. - Forget it.

927
01:20:59.980 --> 01:21:02.260
Tell me. how is mother?

928
01:21:04.380 --> 01:21:06.380
She is very serious. big brother.

929
01:21:07.420 --> 01:21:10.820
She hasn't closed
her eyes once in two days.

930
01:21:11.500 --> 01:21:15.420
She is as inert as a rock.

931
01:21:16.700 --> 01:21:20.100
Doctors say she's
in a very critical state.

932
01:21:21.220 --> 01:21:23.300
If she doesn't come around..

933
01:21:30.260 --> 01:21:30.860
Go son.

934
01:21:32.300 --> 01:21:33.260
Go on

935
01:22:11.220 --> 01:22:14.820
"The earth has gone to sleep"

936
01:22:15.140 --> 01:22:18.820
"The skies have gone to sleep"

937
01:22:19.140 --> 01:22:26.900
"Deep in the slumber
is the whole world"

938
01:22:27.220 --> 01:22:31.060
"With dreams in her eyes.."

939
01:22:31.220 --> 01:22:35.100
"Rocking you in her arms.."

940
01:22:35.180 --> 01:22:40.820
"Your mother sings
a lullaby for you.."

941
01:22:41.100 --> 01:22:49.100
"So come. sleep.."

942
01:22:49.260 --> 01:22:53.180
"Come. slumber"

943
01:23:07.340 --> 01:23:10.980
"I have no one but you"

944
01:23:11.300 --> 01:23:15.260
"You are my only support"

945
01:23:15.340 --> 01:23:23.140
"Without you. I might do the worst"

946
01:23:23.340 --> 01:23:31.100
"I can't live all by myself. I'll die"

947
01:23:31.180 --> 01:23:39.140
"Take me in your arms. embrace me"

948
01:23:39.380 --> 01:23:49.140
"For God's sake.
Ma. don't make me cry"

949
01:23:49.340 --> 01:23:53.380
"Don't bring me to tears"

950
01:23:53.460 --> 01:23:57.500
"Come to me"

951
01:24:08.140 --> 01:24:09.620
I told you. didn't I?

952
01:24:11.260 --> 01:24:17.060
I hate the sight of you!
Get out! Get out of here!

953
01:24:17.260 --> 01:24:20.260
Get out!

954
01:24:20.260 --> 01:24:20.620
Get out!
Nonsense!
It's a lie. Yograj cannot die!

955
01:24:20.620 --> 01:24:23.020
Nonsense!
It's a lie. Yograj cannot die!

956
01:24:23.100 --> 01:24:24.540
Suraj. please.

957
01:24:24.980 --> 01:24:26.620
You cannot bring alive a dead man.

958
01:24:26.700 --> 01:24:28.300
Police records clearly state that..

959
01:24:28.380 --> 01:24:29.980
..that man died. - In an accident?

960
01:24:30.060 --> 01:24:32.020
Right. - His corpse was not found.

961
01:24:32.180 --> 01:24:34.620
It happens. Suraj.
- It is also possible that..

962
01:24:34.780 --> 01:24:39.460
..this is Yograj's ploy to
evade the police. Look at this.

963
01:24:40.220 --> 01:24:42.740
Not a single picture of his..

964
01:24:43.060 --> 01:24:44.540
..in the entire file.
No proofs. no leads.

965
01:24:44.620 --> 01:24:48.820
Some pages are torn out.
If he is dead. then who did all this?

966
01:24:49.300 --> 01:24:51.060
No matter what the police say..

967
01:24:51.140 --> 01:24:54.380
Yograj cannot die before
my mother's humiliation is avenged.

968
01:24:54.980 --> 01:24:56.020
Relax. Suraj.

969
01:24:56.340 --> 01:24:57.940
I'll request the commissioner for..

970
01:24:58.460 --> 01:25:02.100
..his consent to reopen Yograj's case.

971
01:25:03.540 --> 01:25:05.860
Welcome.

972
01:25:09.020 --> 01:25:13.980
Greetings. Thakur sir.
What brings you to Dharampur?

973
01:25:14.060 --> 01:25:17.500
I couldn't refuse minister
Deshmukh's request.

974
01:25:17.580 --> 01:25:19.020
How are you? - I'm fine.

975
01:25:19.460 --> 01:25:21.380
I hear that you are
planning something..

976
01:25:21.460 --> 01:25:23.140
..unique for the welfare of women.

977
01:25:23.220 --> 01:25:25.460
You have heard it right. - Yes.

978
01:25:26.060 --> 01:25:30.940
When it comes to women's welfare.
I'm always a step ahead - Ok.

979
01:25:31.660 --> 01:25:35.180
I want every spurned and deprived..

980
01:25:35.260 --> 01:25:38.060
..woman to come up.
to hold a standing.

981
01:25:38.140 --> 01:25:38.860
Yes.

982
01:25:38.940 --> 01:25:42.780
I have some program for
their upliftment. - Yes. yes.

983
01:25:43.020 --> 01:25:46.340
Let's see how God helps me. - Sure.

984
01:25:46.420 --> 01:25:48.660
Okay. Salutations. - Salutations.

985
01:25:50.580 --> 01:25:54.860
What about Suraj?
- Suraj? You mean the sun? It set.

986
01:25:55.260 --> 01:25:58.620
I mean at your say-so I finished him.
He is dead.

987
01:25:59.100 --> 01:25:59.700
Good.

988
01:26:04.020 --> 01:26:04.700
Let's go.

989
01:26:09.280 --> 01:26:13.360
Himmat. why did you lie
to him that you killed Suraj?

990
01:26:13.520 --> 01:26:19.600
Had I not lied. he'd have
ripped me apart beyond stitching.

991
01:26:20.120 --> 01:26:22.640
I must see this Suraj
off as soon as possible.

992
01:26:46.420 --> 01:26:48.140
Where is Himmat? - I don't know.

993
01:26:48.220 --> 01:26:50.940
Where is he? - I really don't know.

994
01:26:55.780 --> 01:26:59.340
Save me! Save me. Thakur sir.

995
01:26:59.420 --> 01:27:02.620
Let go of me.
Who are you? - Don't you recognise me?

996
01:27:02.900 --> 01:27:05.580
Then Suraj too won't recognise me.
I'm Himmat.

997
01:27:05.660 --> 01:27:08.140
What farce is this. Himmat?
What has gotten into you?

998
01:27:08.220 --> 01:27:10.860
Save me from the wounded tiger.

999
01:27:10.940 --> 01:27:14.020
Else that Suraj will
give me a funeral.

1000
01:27:15.220 --> 01:27:19.140
Suraj..? But you said.. - I lied.

1001
01:27:19.820 --> 01:27:22.820
I lied. Else you would've skinned me.

1002
01:27:23.900 --> 01:27:26.980
But how did he know
that I know Yograj?

1003
01:27:27.280 --> 01:27:29.360
But why is he looking for Yograj?

1004
01:27:32.920 --> 01:27:34.880
What crime of mine..

1005
01:27:37.800 --> 01:27:40.040
..brings up an enemy like Suraj?

1006
01:27:40.120 --> 01:27:41.480
Where is Himmat?

1007
01:27:43.280 --> 01:27:44.360
Speak.

1008
01:27:45.280 --> 01:27:46.220
Where is Himmat? Speak!

1009
01:27:46.220 --> 01:27:47.180
Where is Himmat? Speak!
Good morning.

1010
01:27:47.180 --> 01:27:47.200
Where is Himmat? Speak!

1011
01:27:47.740 --> 01:27:48.940
Good morning. doctor.

1012
01:27:49.020 --> 01:27:50.420
How are you? - Fine.

1013
01:27:50.500 --> 01:27:51.420
Very good.

1014
01:27:51.500 --> 01:27:54.540
Mr. Raja. you can take
your mother home if you want.

1015
01:27:55.060 --> 01:27:59.220
But you need complete bed rest.
Okay. - Okay.

1016
01:27:59.300 --> 01:28:02.020
She is very weak. Take care. bye.
- Okay. thank you Doctor.

1017
01:28:02.540 --> 01:28:05.740
Shall we. mother?
Let me take you home. - Let's go. son.

1018
01:28:09.620 --> 01:28:10.460
You're back?

1019
01:28:11.620 --> 01:28:12.260
Sapna.

1020
01:28:13.100 --> 01:28:15.580
I was bent on seeing you tonight.

1021
01:28:15.780 --> 01:28:18.260
What for?
- What's come over you. Suraj?

1022
01:28:18.500 --> 01:28:23.260
Me..? Nothing. - Why aren't
you your old self anymore?

1023
01:28:24.020 --> 01:28:28.460
Why do I feel you're trying
to hide something very serious..

1024
01:28:29.060 --> 01:28:31.420
..that you fear might come out
in the open if you keep meeting us?

1025
01:28:32.140 --> 01:28:35.700
Nothing of that sort. Sapna.
It's quite late. go to bed.

1026
01:28:36.020 --> 01:28:37.240
Suraj.

1027
01:28:37.240 --> 01:28:37.460
Suraj.
What kind of a friend are you?
At least wish me happy birthday.

1028
01:28:37.460 --> 01:28:40.400
What kind of a friend are you?
At least wish me happy birthday.

1029
01:28:41.480 --> 01:28:43.280
Is it your birthday?

1030
01:28:45.240 --> 01:28:46.320
Happy birthday.

1031
01:28:47.120 --> 01:28:48.840
May you be blessed with
all the happiness in the world.

1032
01:28:49.120 --> 01:28:50.080
Thanks.

1033
01:28:51.360 --> 01:28:54.960
Would you give me anything I ask for?
- Ask for anything.

1034
01:28:55.040 --> 01:28:56.240
Promise? - Promise.

1035
01:28:56.480 --> 01:28:58.760
You must come tomorrow
for my birthday party.

1036
01:28:59.360 --> 01:29:03.120
That's all? I will come.
- You won't make an excuse. will you?

1037
01:29:03.440 --> 01:29:07.040
You have promised me.
- I will certainly come.

1038
01:29:10.080 --> 01:29:13.280
Hey this is beautiful. Give me
this one. Pack it nicely. yeah? - Hey.

1039
01:29:13.360 --> 01:29:15.440
Why are you showing him that?
Put it away.

1040
01:29:16.040 --> 01:29:18.280
Sorry. sir. That necklace is sold.
Please find another one.

1041
01:29:18.360 --> 01:29:22.200
Sir please. This is the one I like.
I've seen the others.

1042
01:29:22.280 --> 01:29:25.160
If you wish. we can make
another necklace of the same design.

1043
01:29:25.240 --> 01:29:26.560
But that will take some time.

1044
01:29:26.640 --> 01:29:29.240
Today's the birthday and today
I must gift it. Please try something.

1045
01:29:30.720 --> 01:29:33.440
I'll call the gentleman who wanted it.

1046
01:29:33.520 --> 01:29:35.480
Maybe he doesn't want it anymore?
- Thank you.

1047
01:29:35.720 --> 01:29:38.400
Sapna. what do you think
of this place for the party?

1048
01:29:38.640 --> 01:29:42.000
Fantastic! Ma'am this is
the best place that we have. - Okay.

1049
01:29:42.240 --> 01:29:44.320
Lighting and decoration.. - Everything
will be done ma'am. - Hello.

1050
01:29:44.400 --> 01:29:46.280
Sir. this is Mahesh from D.P.
Jewellers.

1051
01:29:47.080 --> 01:29:49.880
You had liked a necklace
and ask me to preserve it for you.

1052
01:29:50.200 --> 01:29:53.240
May I send it home or
will you have it picked up?

1053
01:29:53.520 --> 01:29:56.400
A necklace?
- Have you already forgotten?

1054
01:29:56.680 --> 01:30:01.080
You were here with Mr. Balwant.
Mr. Jugnu and the whole family

1055
01:30:01.160 --> 01:30:04.600
And there was this girl. your guest..
what was her name?

1056
01:30:05.720 --> 01:30:10.400
Sapna! Right. Sapna.
You had chosen it for her.

1057
01:30:10.480 --> 01:30:12.800
Remember. Mr Suraj? - Yes. I remember

1058
01:30:13.920 --> 01:30:17.600
I don't need it anymore.
You may sell it to anyone you wish.

1059
01:30:17.680 --> 01:30:20.160
Okay. You are lucky sir.

1060
01:30:20.800 --> 01:30:21.840
You can have the necklace.

1061
01:30:25.040 --> 01:30:25.760
Yes.

1062
01:30:50.240 --> 01:30:55.680
"It's a lovely evening
and my beloved is with me"

1063
01:30:55.760 --> 01:31:01.280
"It's a lovely evening
and my beloved is with me"

1064
01:31:01.600 --> 01:31:07.240
"What more I could
ask for in my lifetime?"

1065
01:31:07.400 --> 01:31:12.920
"It's a lovely evening
and your beloved is with you"

1066
01:31:13.160 --> 01:31:18.880
"What more can you
want for your love?"

1067
01:31:18.960 --> 01:31:24.680
"It's a lovely evening
and my beloved is with me"

1068
01:31:24.760 --> 01:31:28.600
"Such a lovely evening
and our feelings are young"

1069
01:31:30.320 --> 01:31:35.840
"It's such a lovely evening
and we're young at heart"

1070
01:31:35.920 --> 01:31:41.680
"What better things could
I want for a friendship?"

1071
01:31:41.760 --> 01:31:48.080
"It's a lovely evening
and my beloved is with me"

1072
01:31:50.220 --> 01:31:57.620
"You are like the moonlight.
you are like a fairy.."

1073
01:31:57.700 --> 01:32:01.820
"..for poets. you are so inspiring"

1074
01:32:07.340 --> 01:32:13.020
"The sight of you
drove my heart crazy.."

1075
01:32:13.100 --> 01:32:18.780
"..and thus started a love-story"

1076
01:32:18.860 --> 01:32:22.780
"Colour. beauty and lovely dreams.."

1077
01:32:24.500 --> 01:32:30.100
"I have it all"

1078
01:32:30.380 --> 01:32:36.100
"What more could
I ask for to be happy?"

1079
01:32:36.180 --> 01:32:42.500
"It's a lovely evening
and my beloved is with me"

1080
01:33:07.240 --> 01:33:11.240
"Here's love.
passion and the beloved.."

1081
01:33:13.000 --> 01:33:18.800
"Here's love.
passion and the beloved.."

1082
01:33:30.160 --> 01:33:35.840
"My eyes express what my lips don't.."

1083
01:33:35.920 --> 01:33:41.560
"..my story is different
from everybody else's"

1084
01:33:41.640 --> 01:33:47.360
"I have fallen in love with anyone.."

1085
01:33:47.440 --> 01:33:53.080
"I've never ever allowed
the sweet agony to grip my heart"

1086
01:33:53.160 --> 01:33:57.080
"There's music.
there's melody. there's a song.."

1087
01:33:58.840 --> 01:34:04.160
"There's music.
there's melody. there's a song.."

1088
01:34:04.240 --> 01:34:10.000
"..what more can we want
for a lovely number?"

1089
01:34:10.080 --> 01:34:15.600
"It's a lovely evening
and my beloved is with me"

1090
01:34:15.880 --> 01:34:21.320
"What more could I want in life?"

1091
01:34:21.400 --> 01:34:26.960
"It's a lovely evening
and your beloved is with you"

1092
01:34:27.360 --> 01:34:33.160
"What more could you want in love?"

1093
01:34:45.320 --> 01:34:48.920
Mr Rajpal Thakur.
who is today in our midst..

1094
01:34:49.000 --> 01:34:52.800
..who will tell us how rapists
should be punished. Thakur sir.

1095
01:34:53.280 --> 01:34:58.360
Why does man forget that it
was a woman who gave birth to him?

1096
01:34:59.040 --> 01:35:01.480
Why does he make her
a victim of his lust?

1097
01:35:01.560 --> 01:35:04.920
Why does he outrage her modesty?
Why does he rape her?

1098
01:35:05.320 --> 01:35:09.080
In my opinion. rape is a
more heinous crime than even murder.

1099
01:35:10.320 --> 01:35:12.720
Because in a murder.
a woman dies only once.

1100
01:35:14.400 --> 01:35:19.000
Whereas rape inflicts death
on a woman every day of her life.

1101
01:35:19.920 --> 01:35:25.160
And a woman rues something
for which she was not to blame.

1102
01:35:30.260 --> 01:35:34.900
Woman is the greatest
boon God has granted to man.

1103
01:35:38.220 --> 01:35:42.940
A woman deserves a status
that is equal to God's.

1104
01:35:45.500 --> 01:35:51.020
However. there are monsters who.
blinded by lust..

1105
01:35:51.860 --> 01:35:55.020
try to violate a
woman's sacred honour.

1106
01:35:56.020 --> 01:35:57.780
For men who commits
such heinous crimes..

1107
01:35:57.860 --> 01:35:59.620
..a 7-year prison term is not enough.

1108
01:36:00.460 --> 01:36:02.700
They ought to be paraded..

1109
01:36:02.780 --> 01:36:04.380
..in the streets and shot dead.

1110
01:36:05.280 --> 01:36:06.200
Thank you.

1111
01:36:18.480 --> 01:36:21.200
This chap is Suraj.
the owner of this hotel.

1112
01:36:21.800 --> 01:36:23.760
He's the one who had your file..

1113
01:36:27.920 --> 01:36:30.040
In the applause of the others..

1114
01:36:30.120 --> 01:36:31.640
..I found true
appreciation for myself.

1115
01:36:32.480 --> 01:36:34.680
Your applause.
however. pokes fun at me.

1116
01:36:35.040 --> 01:36:37.120
That's what I think. - And I thought..

1117
01:36:37.200 --> 01:36:40.720
..that your face wasn't in
sync with what you were saying.

1118
01:36:42.120 --> 01:36:45.920
Don't you think shooting such
men will make death easy for them?

1119
01:36:46.320 --> 01:36:48.200
So how should such men be punished?

1120
01:36:49.880 --> 01:36:52.240
A man like that ought
to be tortured to death.

1121
01:36:53.200 --> 01:36:57.480
He ought to be blinded for
casting a lustful look at a woman.

1122
01:36:58.040 --> 01:36:59.960
His hands ought to be severed..

1123
01:37:00.680 --> 01:37:04.200
..the hands that violated
a woman's honour.

1124
01:37:05.160 --> 01:37:09.720
He should be publicly whipped.
so much that..

1125
01:37:09.800 --> 01:37:13.040
..he begs for pardon.

1126
01:37:18.240 --> 01:37:22.480
You have indeed thought
of a great punishment.

1127
01:37:24.160 --> 01:37:25.160
So much of hatred?

1128
01:37:27.160 --> 01:37:30.320
Any special reason
for so much of contempt?

1129
01:37:32.720 --> 01:37:37.720
Do you need a reason to
hold something evil in contempt..

1130
01:37:38.080 --> 01:37:41.000
Thakur. - Thakur sir

1131
01:37:43.400 --> 01:37:45.320
You are indeed an interesting man.

1132
01:37:46.520 --> 01:37:49.160
Your face isn't again
saying what your mouth is.

1133
01:37:50.320 --> 01:37:53.920
A man who speaks the truth
isn't interesting.. he's bitter.

1134
01:37:57.240 --> 01:38:00.920
Perhaps my face won't
again express what my lips do.

1135
01:38:03.120 --> 01:38:09.560
But I do like people like you.
- But I do not like you at all.

1136
01:38:12.400 --> 01:38:17.080
Why do you think I'm so bad?
This is our very first meeting.

1137
01:38:17.600 --> 01:38:23.200
No. Thakur sir. We are no strangers.
We have already met.

1138
01:38:26.600 --> 01:38:29.920
Where? - I don't know.

1139
01:38:31.480 --> 01:38:32.920
But we have surely met.

1140
01:38:42.280 --> 01:38:44.200
I mean.
- I get it. Himmat.

1141
01:38:44.440 --> 01:38:46.040
This is not your cup of tea.

1142
01:38:47.360 --> 01:38:52.640
You can just watch how I
tame this ferocious tiger of yours.

1143
01:38:54.320 --> 01:38:55.120
Let's go.

1144
01:38:56.800 --> 01:39:01.360
Why don't you tell me?
These fits that mother suffers from..

1145
01:39:01.800 --> 01:39:03.040
..what's the reason?

1146
01:39:03.400 --> 01:39:06.680
As difficult as it
is for me to say it..

1147
01:39:08.680 --> 01:39:12.600
..it'll be more difficult
for you to hear it.

1148
01:39:19.800 --> 01:39:24.360
Many years ago. your mother
went through a terrible incident..

1149
01:39:25.080 --> 01:39:26.720
..I was on duty at the hospital then.

1150
01:39:47.280 --> 01:39:49.840
There was an unfortunate boy who was..

1151
01:39:49.920 --> 01:39:52.000
..separated from
us and abandoned here.

1152
01:39:52.880 --> 01:39:57.160
It was Suraj. wasn't it?

1153
01:39:59.480 --> 01:40:02.840
Big brother! Here I am!

1154
01:40:03.480 --> 01:40:09.040
Raja. Why have you called me here?

1155
01:40:09.120 --> 01:40:11.440
What I want to talk to you..

1156
01:40:12.320 --> 01:40:16.880
..about cannot be discussed
at the mansion nor at your house.

1157
01:40:17.880 --> 01:40:21.160
And I had to drink..

1158
01:40:21.640 --> 01:40:26.560
..because I couldn't have talked
about it in a sober state of mind.

1159
01:40:27.040 --> 01:40:28.120
I'm sorry.

1160
01:40:28.480 --> 01:40:33.680
What's so serious. Raja?
- Raja..? Already?

1161
01:40:35.360 --> 01:40:37.320
Won't you call me little brother?

1162
01:40:40.360 --> 01:40:41.920
Won't you embrace me?

1163
01:40:43.600 --> 01:40:45.200
Won't you hug me?

1164
01:40:50.840 --> 01:40:55.600
Your favors.
your love and your sacrifice..

1165
01:40:55.680 --> 01:41:00.840
I could understand nothing you do.
And today I realize..

1166
01:41:01.160 --> 01:41:06.920
how big the elder brother really is.
What say. brother?

1167
01:41:17.080 --> 01:41:20.600
Despite being brothers.
we have different destinies.

1168
01:41:22.040 --> 01:41:25.480
I get all the happiness
and you get all the sorrows.

1169
01:41:27.080 --> 01:41:34.440
I get the share of the joys..
and you get to share the woes.

1170
01:41:35.840 --> 01:41:37.480
I was the one who got
all of our mother's love.

1171
01:41:38.920 --> 01:41:42.440
And you.. you got only hatred.

1172
01:41:44.760 --> 01:41:50.680
You even pined to
hear mother call you son.

1173
01:41:51.920 --> 01:41:58.160
Brother. when I think of
what you've been through. I..

1174
01:41:59.240 --> 01:42:03.920
There is no problem now. Raja.
I have my brother with me.

1175
01:42:15.520 --> 01:42:19.320
If that is true.
why did Suraj give his letters to you?

1176
01:42:22.240 --> 01:42:26.360
Because he's my brother. Sapna.

1177
01:42:28.000 --> 01:42:29.560
For the sake of their
younger brothers..

1178
01:42:30.240 --> 01:42:33.200
..elder brothers often
sacrifice their joys.

1179
01:42:35.680 --> 01:42:39.760
Sapna. my brother has found
nothing but pain in his lifetime.

1180
01:42:43.680 --> 01:42:49.840
You know how ill-luck
has always followed him.

1181
01:42:51.480 --> 01:42:54.040
How can I pay back a brother
for the sacrifices he has made?

1182
01:42:58.640 --> 01:43:03.440
I want you to help me. Sapna.
Please help me.

1183
01:43:04.600 --> 01:43:08.040
Like I snatched his
mother from him as a child..

1184
01:43:09.840 --> 01:43:13.800
I don't want to snatch
his love from him today.

1185
01:43:14.000 --> 01:43:17.560
Sapna.. Sapna?

1186
01:44:04.440 --> 01:44:08.520
Suraj. will you tell
me the truth? - What?

1187
01:44:11.519 --> 01:44:13.159
Are you in love with me?

1188
01:44:17.640 --> 01:44:21.520
What sort of question is that?
- Straight and simple.

1189
01:44:22.759 --> 01:44:24.439
You were the one who said that..

1190
01:44:24.519 --> 01:44:26.519
..love makes for
a strange relationship.

1191
01:44:27.359 --> 01:44:28.599
That every relationship
in the world is..

1192
01:44:29.160 --> 01:44:30.960
..merged into this one relationship?

1193
01:44:32.679 --> 01:44:33.959
I want to know. Suraj.

1194
01:44:36.280 --> 01:44:39.600
All these letters..
did you write them for me?

1195
01:44:46.480 --> 01:44:48.320
Is love all that matters in life?

1196
01:44:49.080 --> 01:44:50.880
Does friendship amount to nothing?

1197
01:44:52.639 --> 01:44:54.239
How could you even
imagine such a thing?

1198
01:44:54.320 --> 01:44:56.080
What made you think like that?

1199
01:44:56.799 --> 01:44:58.159
Is it because of these letters..?

1200
01:44:58.240 --> 01:45:00.320
Because you see the name "Sapna" here?

1201
01:45:00.400 --> 01:45:02.560
Is there only one Sapna in this world?

1202
01:45:06.280 --> 01:45:08.640
It's a coincidence. The girl I was..

1203
01:45:09.080 --> 01:45:10.560
..in love with was also called Sapna.

1204
01:45:10.840 --> 01:45:14.480
What..? - She couldn't marry me.

1205
01:45:15.000 --> 01:45:16.080
She married someone else.

1206
01:45:17.840 --> 01:45:20.880
Anyway.. how was I
to know that my letters..

1207
01:45:20.959 --> 01:45:22.399
..would help my brother some day?

1208
01:45:27.480 --> 01:45:31.480
You are my best friend. And
you couldn't understand my feelings?

1209
01:45:32.679 --> 01:45:35.279
I'm sorry.

1210
01:45:40.260 --> 01:45:53.580
'Sanskrit chant'

1211
01:45:55.980 --> 01:46:14.780
'Sanskrit chant'

1212
01:46:22.440 --> 01:46:24.280
Yograj!

1213
01:46:28.800 --> 01:46:31.440
What are you doing..?
This is Thakur sir!

1214
01:46:31.520 --> 01:46:34.720
Leave him. Leave him! - Mother.

1215
01:46:35.440 --> 01:46:36.600
Nothing.

1216
01:46:36.680 --> 01:46:39.040
Yograj. - Mother!
It's okay.. I'm sorry sir.

1217
01:46:39.120 --> 01:46:41.280
This is Thakur-sir.
- I'm sorry. Thakur sir

1218
01:46:41.360 --> 01:46:46.040
Mother often has these fits.
She isn't well.

1219
01:46:46.240 --> 01:46:49.760
I am really sorry. Sorry.

1220
01:46:51.320 --> 01:46:56.040
Mother! He's not Yograj. mother.
It's Thakur.

1221
01:46:57.360 --> 01:46:59.760
It's Thakur.
Everything will be all right.

1222
01:46:59.840 --> 01:47:07.160
No. this is not a disguise!
I was burnt! By Suraj!

1223
01:47:07.240 --> 01:47:11.920
I'm glad I went a doctor on time.
As they truly say..

1224
01:47:12.000 --> 01:47:14.080
..doctors are like Gods.
One saved me..

1225
01:47:14.160 --> 01:47:17.280
..and even answered your question.

1226
01:47:17.360 --> 01:47:19.360
A question that always bothered you.

1227
01:47:19.440 --> 01:47:22.440
As to why Suraj is after your blood.

1228
01:47:22.540 --> 01:47:23.860
Gogi.

1229
01:47:25.100 --> 01:47:26.620
When I came to my senses.

1230
01:47:26.700 --> 01:47:30.380
I heard this doctor
saying something about Suraj.

1231
01:47:30.780 --> 01:47:35.420
I then put pressure
on him and got to know..

1232
01:47:35.740 --> 01:47:37.100
You tell him.

1233
01:47:44.260 --> 01:47:46.340
I have a feeling that
this Thakur is Yograj.

1234
01:47:47.020 --> 01:47:49.220
Because whenever we
set out to find Yograj..

1235
01:47:49.300 --> 01:47:51.660
..we come across Thakur.

1236
01:47:52.300 --> 01:47:55.300
Okay. Suraj. On mere suspicion..
- We'll even find the evidence.

1237
01:47:55.700 --> 01:47:59.300
The guilt of a criminal
often implicates him.

1238
01:48:04.900 --> 01:48:06.300
Hello. - - Yograj.

1239
01:48:10.900 --> 01:48:12.900
Which Yograj? - The Yograj..

1240
01:48:13.860 --> 01:48:18.740
..who raped innumerable
girls in this very city..

1241
01:48:19.180 --> 01:48:20.540
..and then slit their throats.

1242
01:48:21.780 --> 01:48:24.220
You've got the wrong number.

1243
01:48:25.260 --> 01:48:26.940
There is no Yograj here.

1244
01:48:27.580 --> 01:48:28.980
This is Thakur Rajveer
Singh's residence.

1245
01:48:30.740 --> 01:48:35.460
Yograj. you can fool the
world as Thakur.. but not me

1246
01:48:36.220 --> 01:48:38.260
I've been looking
for you for many years.

1247
01:48:39.340 --> 01:48:41.860
And here you are.
- Haven't I told you?

1248
01:48:42.420 --> 01:48:44.980
I told you that you
are making a mistake.

1249
01:48:45.220 --> 01:48:47.540
I recognise your voice very well.

1250
01:48:47.740 --> 01:48:51.180
I have evidence of your dirty deeds.

1251
01:48:52.020 --> 01:48:57.180
I want a deal with you for your life.
For just 5 million rupees.

1252
01:48:58.380 --> 01:49:01.540
At 5 this evening.
come to table 10 at..

1253
01:49:01.940 --> 01:49:04.860
..the Royal Club. with the money.

1254
01:49:05.700 --> 01:49:08.740
Or else. I have other
buyers for those pictures.

1255
01:49:09.480 --> 01:49:14.160
Hello..

1256
01:49:28.760 --> 01:49:31.280
If he or any of his men gets there..

1257
01:49:32.040 --> 01:49:35.840
..it means Thakur is indeed Yograj.

1258
01:49:44.680 --> 01:49:49.600
I have taken an oath that
this patriarchal society..

1259
01:49:49.680 --> 01:49:53.800
..which inflicts atrocities on women.
shall have..

1260
01:49:58.080 --> 01:49:59.280
shall..

1261
01:50:02.120 --> 01:50:03.120
shall..

1262
01:50:06.600 --> 01:50:07.680
shall..

1263
01:50:10.600 --> 01:50:11.720
Stop him!

1264
01:50:47.540 --> 01:50:50.820
The first time I met you. I wondered..

1265
01:50:53.220 --> 01:50:59.540
..how a softie like Babu
could sire a fiery son like you.

1266
01:51:01.180 --> 01:51:05.900
And then I got to know..
that you're an illegitimate son.

1267
01:51:09.580 --> 01:51:14.220
What rage! Rage at the truth?

1268
01:51:15.820 --> 01:51:19.420
Suraj. your death
is a certainty today.

1269
01:51:20.540 --> 01:51:24.540
Why? Can't you see?

1270
01:51:26.260 --> 01:51:27.260
Take a good look.

1271
01:51:29.180 --> 01:51:32.540
Today. my face says
what my tongue says.

1272
01:51:33.540 --> 01:51:38.820
Hats off to you. You have
at last got to know that I'm Yograj.

1273
01:51:40.660 --> 01:51:43.340
People are scared of eye-balling.

1274
01:51:43.420 --> 01:51:45.300
Yograj and you had
the temerity to hit him.

1275
01:51:47.220 --> 01:51:49.820
That was a gross miscalculation
you made of my strength.

1276
01:51:50.060 --> 01:51:53.180
You are a coward and a spineless man.

1277
01:51:53.400 --> 01:51:56.040
You do know how to outrage
the modesty of a woman.

1278
01:51:57.120 --> 01:52:02.680
The acid that comes with
the offspring of your outrage..

1279
01:52:03.400 --> 01:52:07.600
..you do not have the courage to face.

1280
01:52:08.400 --> 01:52:10.240
No wonder you've had me tied up..

1281
01:52:10.320 --> 01:52:12.400
..to behave like an eunuch.

1282
01:52:13.560 --> 01:52:14.600
What did you say?

1283
01:52:17.220 --> 01:52:18.260
An eunuch?

1284
01:52:23.900 --> 01:52:28.020
Your very existence defies
what you just said. Suraj.

1285
01:52:30.220 --> 01:52:32.100
You are a spirited man. no doubt.

1286
01:52:34.460 --> 01:52:36.180
You have indeed taken
after your mother.

1287
01:52:38.220 --> 01:52:42.260
Know what?
She was a spirited lady too.

1288
01:52:44.780 --> 01:52:48.980
Like a glass of wine..
she was very intoxicating.

1289
01:52:51.180 --> 01:52:54.820
Like the Full Moon..
she was brimming with youth.

1290
01:52:57.340 --> 01:52:59.660
Like a dish that is boiling..

1291
01:53:01.140 --> 01:53:02.300
..she was hot.

1292
01:53:54.820 --> 01:53:56.620
Leave him.

1293
01:53:57.900 --> 01:53:58.660
Let go!

1294
01:53:59.700 --> 01:54:00.580
Leave.

1295
01:54:01.180 --> 01:54:02.140
Hit him.

1296
01:54:04.020 --> 01:54:05.300
Someone make him let go!

1297
01:54:14.500 --> 01:54:15.420
Get him!

1298
01:54:25.220 --> 01:54:27.420
Not your entire police force..

1299
01:54:27.500 --> 01:54:31.140
..could get your
hands on one unarmed man!

1300
01:54:31.500 --> 01:54:34.180
Shame on you!
0 We are doing our best. Thakur-sir

1301
01:54:34.260 --> 01:54:37.180
I don't want to listen
to anything! Shut up!

1302
01:54:38.700 --> 01:54:40.180
Find him. however you do it.

1303
01:54:40.900 --> 01:54:44.740
Before that dog can bite me.
hack him to pieces. Get that?

1304
01:54:45.060 --> 01:54:46.140
Very well. Thakur sir.

1305
01:54:47.140 --> 01:54:49.460
Get out of that place immediately.

1306
01:54:49.700 --> 01:54:50.980
S.P. Rana knows where you are..

1307
01:54:51.060 --> 01:54:52.980
..and he's out to kill you.
And listen. Suraj..

1308
01:54:53.140 --> 01:54:56.780
Thakur has been exposed
before the police.

1309
01:54:56.980 --> 01:54:59.420
His finger-prints have
proved that he's Yograj.

1310
01:54:59.500 --> 01:55:00.820
But he's absconding.

1311
01:55:04.320 --> 01:55:05.320
Suraj!

1312
01:55:11.520 --> 01:55:13.440
Move out! Leave the car!

1313
01:55:13.760 --> 01:55:15.040
Hey come on!

1314
01:56:17.440 --> 01:56:19.160
Attention. passengers.

1315
01:56:19.240 --> 01:56:22.080
Train on platform on number
one is headed for the yard.

1316
01:56:22.160 --> 01:56:25.000
Passengers are requested
not to board it.

1317
01:56:25.080 --> 01:56:27.440
Come on!
Else. I'll shoot both your sons.

1318
01:56:47.680 --> 01:56:50.920
Faster! The train
must stop only in Delhi!

1319
01:56:59.920 --> 01:57:01.240
Madhav.

1320
01:57:09.960 --> 01:57:11.360
Mother.

1321
01:57:17.640 --> 01:57:19.040
Mother.

1322
01:57:38.200 --> 01:57:39.400
Madhav Singh.

1323
02:00:10.280 --> 02:00:11.240
Mother.

1324
02:00:12.280 --> 02:00:14.840
My son! Suraj.. - Mother!

1325
02:00:15.640 --> 02:00:18.120
No. - Mother.

1326
02:00:20.600 --> 02:00:22.400
Son Suraj.

1327
02:00:23.160 --> 02:00:27.960
My son. I owe you so much

1328
02:00:29.200 --> 02:00:33.960
I could never give you
the love you were entitled to

1329
02:00:36.160 --> 02:00:38.720
Forgive me. my son. - No. Mother

1330
02:00:40.040 --> 02:00:44.920
Don't say such things.
See? I'm happy today..

1331
02:00:45.760 --> 02:00:47.360
I lie in my mother's lap.

1331
